data.description: If you are looking for a gated community in an incredible location with great schools, then welcome home to The Gates at Pates Creek. This community is tucked away off Jonesboro Road and will offer new homes with up to 5 bedrooms featuring brick fronts with shake accents, granite, stainless steel appliances and fireplaces in the family room. All just 4 miles to I-75 and minutes to shopping, dining, parks and recreation. This expansive two-story design features a dramatic formal dining room. Entertaining is easy with an island kitchen overlooking the family room with cozy fireplace. Stay organized with a spacious pantry and butler's pantry. Cabinet color options include gray, white and espresso. A guest bedroom and full bath round out the main floor. Upstairs you'll find a second family room, two additional bedrooms and full bath, laundry, and a private bedroom suite with sitting area, oversized closet and spa-like bath. And you will never be too far from home with Home Is Connected.® Your new home is built with an industry leading suite of smart home products that keep you connected with the people and place you value most. Photos used for illustrative purposes and do not depict actual home.
